## Field Reference

### Field Coverage Matrix

| Field | unitOverview | unit(id) | Type | Notes |
|-------|:------------:|:--------:|------|-------|
| **Core Identifiers** |
| `id` | ✓ | ✓ | UUID | Primary key |
| `unitCode` | ✓ | ✓ | String | ZEREZ unit code (e.g., "ZE-RTTR-CRN5-0001") |
| `modelName` | ✓ | ✓ | String | Product model name |
| `modelNumber` | ✓ | ✓ | String | Model number |
| **Manufacturer & Classification** |
| `manufacturerName` | ✓ | ✗ | String | **Only in unitOverview!** |
| `manufacturerId` | ✗ | ✓ | UUID | Must resolve via tenant query |
| `primaryEnergySource` | ✓ | ✗ | Enum | **Only in unitOverview!** |
| `category` | ✓ | ✗ | Enum | **Only in unitOverview!** |
| **Certificate Information** |
| `certificateNumber` | ✓ | ✗ | String | **Only in unitOverview!** |
| `certificateIssueDate` | ✓ | ✗ | DateTime | |
| `certificateValidityStatusName` | ✓ | ✗ | String | |
| `certificateNormIssueDateDescriptions` | ✓ | ✗ | String | |
| **Power Specifications** |
| `maxActivePower` | ✓ | ✓ | Float | kW - Both queries (detailed is more accurate) |
| `ratedActivePower` | ✗ | ✓ | Float | kW - **Only in unit(id)!** |
| `maxApparentPower` | ✗ | ✓ | Float | kVA - **Only in unit(id)!** |
| `ratedApparentPower` | ✗ | ✓ | Float | kVA - **Only in unit(id)!** |
| **Electrical Parameters** |
| `ratedVoltage` | ✗ | ✓ | Float | V - **Only in unit(id)!** |
| `ratedCurrent` | ✗ | ✓ | Float | A - **Only in unit(id)!** |
| `shortCircuitPeakCurrent` | ✗ | ✓ | Float | A - **Only in unit(id)!** |
| `initialShortCircuitAlternatingCurrent` | ✗ | ✓ | Float | A - **Only in unit(id)!** |
| **Compliance** |
| `isVerified` | ✓ | ✓ | Boolean | Can be null! |
| `is4105` | ✓ | ✓ | Boolean | VDE-AR-N 4105 compliance - Can be null! |
| **Metadata** |
| `createdAt` | ✓ | ✓ | DateTime | |
| `modifiedAt` | ✓ | ✓ | DateTime | |
| `validityStartDate` | ✓ | ✗ | DateTime | Certificate validity |
| `validityEndDate` | ✓ | ✗ | DateTime | Certificate validity |

### German Technical Terms Reference

| English | German | Field Name |
|---------|--------|------------|
| Rated Active Power | Bemessungswirkleistung | `ratedActivePower` |
| Max Active Power | Maximale Wirkleistung | `maxActivePower` |
| Rated Apparent Power | Bemessungsscheinleistung | `ratedApparentPower` |
| Max Apparent Power | Maximale Scheinleistung | `maxApparentPower` |
| Rated Voltage | Bemessungsspannung | `ratedVoltage` |
| Rated Current | Bemessungsstrom | `ratedCurrent` |
| Peak Short-Circuit Current | Stoßkurzschlussstrom | `shortCircuitPeakCurrent` |
| Initial Short-Circuit AC | Anfangs-Kurzschlusswechselstrom | `initialShortCircuitAlternatingCurrent` |
| Fast Voltage Change | Schnelle Spannungsänderung | `fastVoltageChange*` |
| Flicker Coefficient | Flimmerfaktor | `systemFlickerCoefficientCY*` |
| Voltage Variation Factor | Spannungsänderungsfaktor | `operation*VoltageVariationFactor*` |

